text: Saifuzzaman Chowdhury Jewel is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Faridpur-2. ==Career== Jewel was elected to parliament from Faridpur-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. He is the Joint Secretary of Parliament Members' Club. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
